org.embulk.plugin

Class InjectedPluginSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.embulk.plugin.InjectedPluginSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PluginSource

    public class InjectedPluginSource
extends java.lang.Object
implements PluginSource
    InjectedPluginSource loads plugins bound by Guice. This plugin source is intended to be used in test cases. Plugins need to be bound to Binder following: // Module public void configure(Binder binder) { InjectedPluginSource.registerPluginTo(InputPluginclass, "my", MyInputPlugin.class); }
